{"tid":2285093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：時間會證明1月誰就任 白宮官員：籌劃第二任期","createTime":"2020-11-13T22:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T15:22:04.000Z","uid":227801,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bad6c510cedc2407d535d5cdd8e57e02ba90bc74","tid":2285093,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T22:52:45.000Z","msg":"注意: 小心蘋果日報用詞來自美國主流媒體<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201114/XVHPZTAX4ZFPPDZGXBCSJ4YXGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201114%2FXVHPZTAX4ZFPPDZGXBCSJ4YXGA%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=28a6da34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201114%2FXVHPZTAX4ZFPPDZGXBCSJ4YXGA%2F&h=9449b218\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201114/XVHPZTAX4ZFPPDZGXBCSJ4YXGA/</a><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n特朗普周五在白宮發言時表示，時間會證明1月誰人就任總統。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周五在白宮就「神速行動」（Operation Warp Speed）舉行工作會議，之後會在玫瑰園就武漢肺炎疫苗研發進展發言，是他在拜登上周六宣佈勝選後，首次公開發言。特朗普政府5月宣佈「神速行動」，由政府和私人藥廠合作快速研發抗疫藥物。特朗普在演說中續以「中國病毒」稱呼武漢肺炎，自詡促成武肺疫苗快速研發，指其他總統可能需時多四倍，說輝瑞武肺疫苗快將獲得緊急使用授權，期望到明年4月武肺疫苗可供美國全民接種。他說其政府無論如何不會以「封鎖」方式抗疫。他發言後沒有接受記者提名。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周五較早時在Twitter發文，表示周六可能會「順道出席」華盛頓一個支持者集會。<br />\n<br />\n同時，白宮一名官員周五表示，白宮繼續籌劃特朗普第二任期。白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）向霍士財經網絡表示，「我們尋求可核實、可認證的選票，以及調查越來越多證人宣誓下作出的選舉欺詐指控」。他表示，現時談論拜登對華貿易政策會如何如何是毫無意義。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"05c98ddd13b510cc709c08b1d1beab6a0530b731","tid":2285093,"uid":18569,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T22:56:58.000Z","msg":"白宮繼續籌劃特朗普第二任期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325beab779b84b28b51803c2fe92df8f394c6c60","tid":2285093,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:00:30.000Z","msg":"冇乜可能，我登必勝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0c4df93a4f340bff60750f819822854b367020","tid":2285093,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8a6f458106a16dfe306d133a1a94a869b6af66","tid":2285093,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7f6cef96a787b850648cfa14aa226f2f327583","tid":2285093,"uid":137480,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPNNmyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPNNmyj.jpg&h=56a64ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"450f0c79f88e0cbbb7838f86b6ac77a55e49ddd7","tid":2285093,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae721896bfbd16df3247f5cf3cbe22198e8c514","tid":2285093,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95beef42ea9631e82299f2e45399ac89987ffaf6","tid":2285093,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T23